1 G.S. 122C-3(11)a., and others, as defined in G.S. 122C-3(11)b., may initiate
2 a new petition for inpatient commitment as provided in this Part. If the
3 respondent is committed as an inpatient, the outpatient commitment shall be
4 terminated and notice sent by the clerk of court in the county where the
5 respondent is committed as an inpatient to the clerk of court of the county
